Let's say work for now.

20
00:02:35,120 --> 00:02:35,880
It's sorted.

21
00:02:36,200 --> 00:02:37,360
You're off next week.

22
00:02:37,480 --> 00:02:37,880
You'll only one bit of

23
00:02:37,960 --> 00:02:39,160
dubbing work to do, for a commercial.

24
00:02:39,320 --> 00:02:40,480
A fifteen-second version

25
00:02:40,600 --> 00:02:41,480
and a thirty-second version.

26
00:02:41,640 --> 00:02:42,720
Three hours at most.

27
00:02:46,240 --> 00:02:47,160
We can talk about personal stuff now?

28
00:02:51,800 --> 00:02:53,520
It's the guy I told you about.

29
00:02:53,960 --> 00:02:54,840
So it's him after all.

30
00:02:56,440 --> 00:02:57,680
When do I get to meet him?

31
00:02:57,960 --> 00:02:59,160
I'm an old hand at this stuff.

32
00:02:59,320 --> 00:03:00,760
Put him in front of me and I'll size him up.

33
00:03:00,920 --> 00:03:02,080
I'll help you check if he's sincere.

34
00:03:02,840 --> 00:03:03,680
He's not a smooth talker like you.

35
00:03:03,840 --> 00:03:05,600
I'm sure you'll be hard on him.

36
00:03:06,560 --> 00:03:07,920
The general's wife admits defeat for the general

37
00:03:08,079 --> 00:03:10,000
before he has even gone into battle.

38
00:03:10,280 --> 00:03:11,560
What general?

39
00:03:11,560 --> 00:03:13,400
He's a researcher.

40
00:03:14,360 --> 00:03:15,000
I didn't forget the story

41
00:03:15,120 --> 00:03:16,240
of how you two met, you know.

42
00:03:16,800 --> 00:03:18,960
Naming really is a big deal.

43
00:03:19,200 --> 00:03:20,360
A good name

44
00:03:20,520 --> 00:03:22,960
helped him meet his future wife.

45
00:03:26,960 --> 00:03:27,880
I'm happy for you.

46
00:03:28,200 --> 00:03:30,560
I wish you great success in both your career and love-life.

47
00:03:31,320 --> 00:03:32,160
Career?

48
00:03:33,160 --> 00:03:34,160
Miss Shi Yi.

49
00:03:34,320 --> 00:03:35,800
Congratulations on the award.

50
00:03:37,520 --> 00:03:38,480
To be precise, it's a nomination.

51
00:03:38,600 --> 00:03:39,120
But they all say

52
00:03:39,240 --> 00:03:40,440
it's a sure thing for you this time.

53
00:03:40,920 --> 00:03:41,960
