59
00:04:00,920 --> 00:04:01,440
Hello?

60
00:04:02,320 --> 00:04:03,120
It's me.

61
00:04:04,600 --> 00:04:06,920
What time did you start work today?

62
00:04:08,440 --> 00:04:09,320
1 pm.

63
00:04:10,160 --> 00:04:12,360
