75
00:04:36,520 --> 00:04:37,520
Have you taken any medicine?

76
00:04:38,480 --> 00:04:39,400
No, I haven't.

77
00:04:39,960 --> 00:04:41,560
Then hang up now. Go take your medicine.

78
00:04:42,159 --> 00:04:42,840
Right now?

79
00:04:43,000 --> 00:04:43,880
Yes.

80
00:04:44,800 --> 00:04:46,520
There's no medicine around me now.

81
00:04:47,320 --> 00:04:48,120
You don't have any

82
00:04:48,120 --> 00:04:49,320
regular medicine with you?

83
00:05:00,520 --> 00:05:01,800
How are you here?

84
00:05:03,160 --> 00:05:03,840
I'm back.

85
00:05:05,520 --> 00:05:06,320
Give me a minute!

86
00:05:07,040 --> 00:05:10,990
