87
00:05:11,810 --> 00:05:14,370
♫With all my strength♫

88
00:05:14,730 --> 00:05:18,480
♫To find traces of you♫

89
00:05:18,520 --> 00:05:19,280
I'm gonna head off.

90
00:05:20,080 --> 00:05:21,200
We're not done talking about the award thing yet!

91
00:05:21,200 --> 00:05:22,080
We'll talk over the phone!

92
00:05:21,460 --> 00:05:23,220
♫Spring flowers and autumn moon♫

93
00:05:22,560 --> 00:05:23,840
There's no need to rush,

94
00:05:23,220 --> 00:05:25,370
♫Hidden in my heart♫

95
00:05:24,000 --> 00:05:25,320
