96
00:05:26,190 --> 00:05:29,000
♫Write words for you♫

97
00:05:29,780 --> 00:05:32,730
♫Tenderly and carefully♫

98
00:05:32,900 --> 00:05:40,420
[Recording Studio]

99
00:05:34,420 --> 00:05:38,580
♫Rewrite the end of the past♫

100
00:05:37,960 --> 00:05:38,840
Why did you come back?

101
00:05:38,960 --> 00:05:41,409
♫Let the story continue♫

102
00:05:39,000 --> 00:05:40,400
And without telling me in advance!

103
00:05:41,820 --> 00:05:44,380
♫You're in my dreams♫

104
00:05:42,200 --> 00:05:43,920
I wanted to surprise you.

105
00:05:45,210 --> 00:05:48,070
♫It's getting clearer and clearer♫

106
00:05:46,640 --> 00:05:48,400
Are you still leaving tonight?

107
00:05:48,340 --> 00:05:51,320
♫When the heart beats, one, two, three, four♫

108
00:05:49,960 --> 00:05:50,960
Where to?

109
00:05:51,490 --> 00:05:53,110
♫It starts to tremble♫

110
00:05:51,600 --> 00:05:53,560
I mean, besides seeing me tonight,

111
00:05:53,250 --> 00:05:56,950
♫The rhythm of love is composed for you♫

112
00:05:53,680 --> 00:05:54,920
have you got anything else you need to do?

113
00:05:56,400 --> 00:05:57,560
Tonight,

114
00:05:57,240 --> 00:06:00,420
♫Go to the end of the world with you♫

115
00:05:57,560 --> 00:05:58,280
I don't have anything

116
00:05:58,280 --> 00:05:59,360
besides seeing you.

117
00:05:59,760 --> 00:06:01,240
My mission tonight is to

118
00:06:00,420 --> 00:06:03,190
♫And be your companion for a lifetime♫

119
00:06:01,400 --> 00:06:02,440
take you home.

120
00:06:03,330 --> 00:06:05,650
♫When every second of time♫

121
00:06:05,650 --> 00:06:07,600
♫Becomes precious♫

122
00:06:06,280 --> 00:06:07,480
Let's go then.

123
00:06:07,600 --> 00:06:09,140
♫Because of you♫

124
00:06:09,000 --> 00:06:10,040
I'll carry it for you.

125
00:06:09,140 --> 00:06:12,180
♫I know what heartache feels like♫

126
00:06:12,780 --> 00:06:15,890
♫Forever and ever is like a dream♫

127
00:06:16,310 --> 00:06:20,140
♫I'll still be with you♫

128
00:07:00,160 --> 00:07:00,680
Hello?

129
00:07:00,800 --> 00:07:01,560
Shi Yi.

130
00:07:02,040 --> 00:07:03,280
I just saw you

131
00:07:03,400 --> 00:07:04,760
and your chemistry professor.

132
00:07:05,160 --> 00:07:05,480
But

133
00:07:05,640 --> 00:07:07,040
I didn't get a good look at him.

134
00:07:07,760 --> 00:07:08,480
Is he handsome?

135
00:07:09,440 --> 00:07:10,800
I'll talk to you later.

136
00:07:11,080 --> 00:07:11,560
Good night.

137
00:07:18,280 --> 00:07:19,800
You still have work to do this late?

138
00:07:20,480 --> 00:07:20,920
No.

139
00:07:21,000 --> 00:07:22,280
Meilin was just saying good night.

140
00:07:30,640 --> 00:07:31,520
Uncle Lin.

141
00:07:31,840 --> 00:07:32,880
We always see each other,

142
00:07:33,040 --> 00:07:34,320
but I don't know your name yet.

143
00:07:34,840 --> 00:07:35,520
Zhou Lin.

144
00:07:36,320 --> 00:07:37,480
Your last name is also Zhou.

145
00:07:37,920 --> 00:07:39,080
Isn't Uncle Lin's nephew

146
